 Phantom Vibration Syndrome is a relatively new psychological phenomenon 

00:01:18.039 --> 00:01:20.909
 Where you think you felt your phone was shaking, while it did not vibrate. 

00:01:20.909 --> 00:01:23.679
 In a study, 89% of those who underwent it said 

00:01:23.679 --> 00:01:25.709
 They face this at least once every two weeks. 

00:01:25.709 --> 00:01:30.419
 It seems that our minds now explain any accentuation as a real vibration of our phones. 

00:01:30.419 --> 00:01:31.759
 As far as the madness of the subject seems, 

